title: Where can I find the official android 11 wallpaper? My 3a has updated to 11, but no new wallpapers.
content:
Hello, I'm Trying to get the official android 11 wallpapers. I don't want to download user created versions, I presumed official ones would come included in the android 11 update but they aren't in the wallpaper section... Any advice?

Thanks.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 3a
